data.description: Seller is offering $7,500 for the buyer to use for a rate buydown or closing costs. Come home to cute!  Enjoy your front porch and rear patio for outdoor living.  The open plan features the primary suite on the main level and a loft and two generous secondary bedrooms on the upper level.  The kitchen to family room flow offers great natural light and room to gather.  Sited adjacent to the cul de sac you have great privacy and the neighborhood offers a pool, clubhouse and playground.  Ready for a quick close, this can be your home very soon.
